DGRID AI GATEWAY CONFIGURATION
DGrid API Key (Obtain from DGrid API Key Console)
DGRID_API_KEY=your_real_dgrid_api_key_here

Model Configuration
Example models: openai/gpt-4o, anthropic/claude-3-opus
DEFAULT_MODEL=openai/gpt-4o

DGrid Endpoint (Default)
DGRID_BASE_URL=https://api.dgrid.ai/v1

Swarm & Agent Identity
Unique identifier for the agentic rail
AGENT_ID=agent_dgrid_01
SWARM_CELL_ID=your_cell_id_from_tashi_console

Local Server Settings
PORT=3000
DEBUG=dgrid:*
